description: nmrpflash uses Netgear's NMRP protocol to flash a new firmware image to a compatible device. It has been successfully used with the Netgear D7000, DNG3700v2, EX2700, EX6100v2, EX6120, EX6150v2, EX8000, R6020, R6080, R6100, R6220, R6400, R7000, R7000P R6800, R8000, R8000P, R8500, WNDR3800, WNDR4300, WNDR4500v3 WNR3500, but is likely to be compatible with many other Netgear devices as well.
